Delish. The chipotle adds a nice kick. For a moist burger, be sure to avoid ground turkey made from "all breast meat." You want a mix of dark and white for more fat and flavor. And for even more spice, try topping these with the chipotle mayo from the "turkey wraps with chipotle mayo" recipe on this site. Yum.

