Rating: 3
Great way to add flavor to turkey burgers. We make these regularly and keep a few pre-formed burgers in the freezer for quick meals. We make them round and use with standard buns (or English muffins) and condiments. Also add extra chipotle - about 1 T. Combining the extra lean and dark ground turkey cuts the fat but keeps the burgers juicy.

